news.title: Elon Musk Is Responsible For Palantir Stock Rally, Jim Cramer Says - Palantir Technologies Inc Ordinary Shares - Class A  ( NASDAQ:PLTR )
news.content: Palantir Technologies Inc PLTR can thank Elon Musk for its 275% year-to-date gain, according to Jim Cramer. What To Know: Palantir, which rallied nearly 50% over just the past month, maybe the only stock outshining Nvidia Corp NVDA this year, Cramer said Tuesday on CNBC's "Squawk On The Street."
